text: Duscaraitraa narai duscaraitra purausara babe, arau duscaraitra purausa duscaraitraa naraira babe; anahate saccaraitraa narai saccaraitra purausara babe arau saccaraitra purausa saccaraitraa naraira babe. Manuhe yi kaya se'iborara saite te'omloka samparkahina; te'omlokara babe ache ksama arau sanmanajanaka jiraika
